since she didn't do anything, right?

5
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,449
Gosh, I doubt that.
She's the victim.

6
00:00:14,919 --> 00:00:15,919
What are people saying?

7
00:00:15,919 --> 00:00:20,329
We're asking our listeners
for the movie of their life.

8
00:00:20,329 --> 00:00:24,260
We're getting a lot of other texts
that aren't movie recommendations.

9
00:00:24,260 --> 00:00:25,760
"Other texts"?

10
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:29,629
From number 2332,
"Ha Jin, cheer up!"

11
00:00:29,899 --> 00:00:34,570
